Radio Fenriz Garage was created by Loudeath Studio on 22 July 2020 in Bali Indonesia. It was inspired by Radio Fenriz a radio/mixtape program in Soundcloud by Fenriz (half of the duo of Black metal band, Darkthrone). As well, it was inspired by the logo of Paradise Garage a discotheque in New York City which is notable in the history of modern dance and pop music, and as LGBT/nightclub cultures.
Made of these two different things, Radio Fenriz Garage has become really fun visually.
